rComments: Despite it being her first time teaching the course, I believe Emily MacLeod is a great professor. Although the concepts in this course were tricky, she made the material more approachable. She was understanding and she genuinely cared for her students' concerns. Not only admirable from a professional standpoint, but she is a genuinely nice person.

Dr. Macleod is a new prof. i believe this is her first time teaching this course. You can tell she's a bit nervous sometimes, but she tried really hard to explain the concepts and was very helpful during the office hours. the exams were a bit hard but grades were curved I believe.
